        <h3 style='text-align: center; margin-bottom:15px'>About</h3>
        <p style='margin-left:10px; margin-right:10px;'>
            Hello! My name is Henry. I'm a Junior Computer Scientist Major
            at The University of Maryland. I created this website for Art and Activism
